{"tid":703990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人個髮旋好少頭髮","createTime":"2018-06-16T05:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T05:01:57.000Z","uid":128414,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7273db9a1b7bcd9ba3123961b4c9e0132943f33c","tid":703990,"uid":128414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/134234_2f6163238c1be1e567f7806471e42624.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F134234_2f6163238c1be1e567f7806471e42624.png&h=ed621776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係甩頭髮 係髮旋特別疏<br />\n做過頭髮分析 我其他部位 一個毛孔有3，4條頭髮<br />\n但髮旋位一個毛孔得1-2條<br />\n頭皮有少少敏感同有角質<br />\n<br />\n最慘係呀哥都有類似情況但估唔到我都有<br />\n唔似係遺傳 我呀媽/呀爸果邊都無人有甩頭髮<br />\n但偏偏我同我呀哥都有髮旋少頭髮既問題<br />\n<br />\n而家頭髮產品既人建議我用 peel mask 清下角質<br />\n試用防脫髮洗頭水 同埋 洗頭要過兩次洗頭水<br />\n<br />\n希望會有改善<br />\n唉 好彩人生得高 平時無咩人睇到"},{"pid":"427a356dee4ba21d6ec7ff5550b4b5213e075ba4","tid":703990,"uid":3682,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"禿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0dfdfeb4e32bf9e51cb1b9fa1963338d44cbaf","tid":703990,"uid":99024,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"咁都唔係甩頭髮<br />\n唔好呃自己啦"},{"pid":"33ef3063e051c12e58f28bcea21fd3b033d3e61c","tid":703990,"uid":127202,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"啲人地中海都係由個轉開始禿起之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a93ccdedb9b065747e5a9f573ca9c528586efb","tid":703990,"uid":8167,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"有啲人脫髮係前額脫先 <br />\n有啲係頭頂脫先"},{"pid":